{"tid":216343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]我阿哥想跣我一獲,點知比我串返轉頭","createTime":"2017-04-25T05:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T10:55:52.000Z","uid":39643,"like":13,"dislike":240,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f338e55692a37859dd92bd4bfdd3746b0791729","tid":216343,"uid":39643,"like":2,"dislike":39,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的.小弟姓曹,屋企本身都有D錢<br />\n都算係一個2世祖...而且我天資聰穎...<br />\n又有錢又有才華重要靚仔...連我都有少少覺得呢個世界唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係呢個世界無完美...我阿爸好鬼風流...我對上重有3個阿哥...對下重有十鳩幾個細佬..<br />\n阿爸死左分起家產上黎我都唔知分得幾多...<br />\n就係前幾年...阿爸死左...間上市公司分左比我2哥(因為大哥都死左)...<br />\n但係2哥嫉妒我又有才華又靚仔...之後條友就成日搞鳩我...<br />\n重調鬼左我去D濕鳩部門...<br />\n就係頭先佢又諗埋D屎橋想黎跣我...<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2哥 :喂,細佬,聽講你吟詩作對咩都識嫁喎<br />\n我:過獎...識少少咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2哥:咁呢有個大客呢就話想你幫佢諗句RAP黎做佢廣告口號..<br />\n<br />\n我屌...我地又唔係廣告公司做乜鳩要幫人諗廣告口號啊...食飽飯冇屎痾?<br />\n一睇就知道又係我呢個腦殘2哥諗既ON9橋..<br />\n<br />\n2哥:係啊...我想你係7步之內諗好佢...如果你因為咁得失個客我會炒左你<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候...我真係好想笑出黎...個情況就好似夜神月對N最後個場既夜神月咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=86RtToAZF-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D86RtToAZF-c&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fba6482b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=86RtToAZF-c</a><br />\n咩你真係以為我唔識RAP淨係識D濕鳩吟詩作對咩??<br />\n<br />\n之後我就用7步RAP左句:<br />\n「煮豆持作羹，漉菽以為汁。萁在釜下燃，豆在釜中泣。本自同根生，相煎何太急？」<br />\n我屌...我真係好佩服自己既才華...點解個天要咁唔公平..生得我咁靚仔又咁醒...<br />\n又可以交貨又可以串佢無兄弟情...睇黎佢見到我咁勁...之後應該都唔會搞鳩我嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只係見到我2哥聽到O晒...最後我都唔阻佢...揮一揮衣袖 不帶走一片雲彩..."},{"pid":"3d9d56ab9f8d9b3a919a42178b5a5fb98fc5e258","tid":216343,"uid":8117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cb66c97008c0c447b88923bbaa20d5ed0694d6","tid":216343,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"850921e7fab73e188d764471b60263327978e187","tid":216343,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時去紅舘開show？<br />\n比D黃牛飛我ok？"},{"pid":"ee0711059e3c6b976256a16a4c8db83fbadd89c3","tid":216343,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾時去紅館開show？<br />\n比D黃牛飛我ok？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"015a9291c03de4679512b1c4f15b3f244bb83a67","tid":216343,"uid":68988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62a567c0ecfd732e75cd0d349e9a138f22006c7","tid":216343,"uid":54667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"算把啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf03bca68d7188729a826f7356f8d60752deaaf","tid":216343,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"😨"},{"pid":"6ea9080a1096b42f7435bd2efe3d0e05fe53124e","tid":216343,"uid":69064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"e427daa5f98e8b64fda4dd256093bc50e78f2c09","tid":216343,"uid":34299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e79db5632a3b5bb166b582988e46b0c3333c21c","tid":216343,"uid":7814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"9f3d489d765956f58f8154bceb3e1478fdc16839","tid":216343,"uid":1195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"